{
  "video_id": "J6--CMhcCfQ",
  "title": "Elliot Krane: The mystery of chronic pain",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 17259.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a pediatrician and an anesthesiologist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17260.0,
      "end_time": 19260.0,
      "text": "so I put children to sleep for a living."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19260.0,
      "end_time": 21260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21260.0,
      "end_time": 24260.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m an academic, so I put audiences to sleep for free."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24260.0,
      "end_time": 28260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28260.0,
      "end_time": 30260.0,
      "text": "But what I actually mostly do"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "is I manage the pain management service"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 35260.0,
      "text": "at the Packard Children&#39;s Hospital up at Stanford in Palo Alto."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35260.0,
      "end_time": 37260.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s from the experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37260.0,
      "end_time": 39260.0,
      "text": "from about 20 or 25 years of doing that"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 41260.0,
      "text": "that I want to bring to you the message this morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41260.0,
      "end_time": 43260.0,
      "text": "that pain is a disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43260.0,
      "end_time": 45260.0,
      "text": "Now most of the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45260.0,
      "end_time": 47260.0,
      "text": "you think of pain as a symptom of a disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47260.0,
      "end_time": 49260.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s true most of the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49260.0,
      "end_time": 52260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the symptom of a tumor or an infection"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 52260.0,
      "end_time": 54260.0,
      "text": "or an inflammation or an operation."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 54260.0,
      "end_time": 57260.0,
      "text": "But about 10 percent of the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57260.0,
      "end_time": 60260.0,
      "text": "after the patient has recovered from one of those events,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 60260.0,
      "end_time": 62260.0,
      "text": "pain persists."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62260.0,
      "end_time": 64259.0,
      "text": "It persists for months"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 64260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66260.0,
      "text": "and oftentimes for years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66260.0,
      "end_time": 68260.0,
      "text": "and when that happens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68260.0,
      "end_time": 70260.0,
      "text": "it is its own disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 70260.0,
      "end_time": 73260.0,
      "text": "And before I tell you about how it is that we think that happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 73260.0,
      "end_time": 75260.0,
      "text": "and what we can do about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 75260.0,
      "end_time": 78260.0,
      "text": "I want to show you how it feels for my patients."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 78260.0,
      "end_time": 80260.0,
      "text": "So imagine, if you will,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 80260.0,
      "end_time": 82260.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;m stroking your arm with this feather,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 85260.0,
      "text": "as I&#39;m stroking my arm right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 85260.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "Now, I want you to imagine"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 87260.0,
      "end_time": 89260.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;m stroking it with this."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 89260.0,
      "end_time": 91260.0,
      "text": "Please keep your seat."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 91260.0,
      "end_time": 93260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 93260.0,
      "end_time": 95260.0,
      "text": "A very different feeling."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 95260.0,
      "end_time": 97260.0,
      "text": "Now what does it have to do with chronic pain?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 97260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "Imagine, if you will, these two ideas together."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 102260.0,
      "text": "Imagine what your life would be like"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 102260.0,
      "end_time": 105260.0,
      "text": "if I were to stroke it with this feather,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 105260.0,
      "end_time": 107260.0,
      "text": "but your brain was telling you"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 107260.0,
      "end_time": 109260.0,
      "text": "that this is what you are feeling --"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 109260.0,
      "end_time": 112260.0,
      "text": "and that is the experience of my patients with chronic pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 112260.0,
      "end_time": 114260.0,
      "text": "In fact, imagine something even worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 114260.0,
      "end_time": 117260.0,
      "text": "Imagine I were to stroke your child&#39;s arm with this feather,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 117260.0,
      "end_time": 119260.0,
      "text": "and their brain [was] telling them"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 119260.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "that they were feeling this hot torch."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "That was the experience of my patient, Chandler,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 126260.0,
      "text": "whom you see in the photograph."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 126260.0,
      "end_time": 128259.0,
      "text": "As you can see, she&#39;s a beautiful, young woman."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 128258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "text": "She was 16 years old last year when I met her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 133260.0,
      "text": "and she aspired to be a professional dancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 133260.0,
      "end_time": 135260.0,
      "text": "And during the course of one of her dance rehearsals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 135260.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "she fell on her outstretched arm and sprained her wrist."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 140260.0,
      "text": "Now you would probably imagine, as she did,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 140260.0,
      "end_time": 142260.0,
      "text": "that a wrist sprain is a trivial event"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 144260.0,
      "text": "in a person&#39;s life."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 144260.0,
      "end_time": 146260.0,
      "text": "Wrap it in an ACE bandage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 146260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "take some ibuprofen for a week or two,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 148260.0,
      "end_time": 150260.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s the end of the story."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 150260.0,
      "end_time": 153260.0,
      "text": "But in Chandler&#39;s case, that was the beginning of the story."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 154260.0,
      "end_time": 156260.0,
      "text": "This is what her arm looked like"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 156260.0,
      "end_time": 159260.0,
      "text": "when she came to my clinic about three months after her sprain."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 159260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "You can see that the arm is discolored,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 161260.0,
      "end_time": 163260.0,
      "text": "purplish in color."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 163260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "It was cadaverically cold to the touch."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 167260.0,
      "text": "The muscles were frozen, paralyzed --"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 167260.0,
      "end_time": 170260.0,
      "text": "dystonic is how we refer to that."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 170260.0,
      "end_time": 173260.0,
      "text": "The pain had spread from her wrist to her hands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 173260.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "to her fingertips, from her wrist up to her elbow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "almost all the way to her shoulder."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 180260.0,
      "text": "But the worst part was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 180260.0,
      "end_time": 183260.0,
      "text": "not the spontaneous pain that was there 24 hours a day."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 186260.0,
      "text": "The worst part was that she had allodynia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 186260.0,
      "end_time": 189260.0,
      "text": "the medical term for the phenomenon that I just illustrated"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 189260.0,
      "end_time": 191260.0,
      "text": "with the feather and with the torch."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 191260.0,
      "end_time": 193260.0,
      "text": "The lightest touch of her arm --"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 193260.0,
      "end_time": 195260.0,
      "text": "the touch of a hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 195260.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "the touch even of a sleeve, of a garment, as she put it on --"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 202260.0,
      "text": "caused excruciating, burning pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 202260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "How can the nervous system get this so wrong?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "How can the nervous system"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 209260.0,
      "text": "misinterpret an innocent sensation"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 211260.0,
      "text": "like the touch of a hand"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 211260.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "and turn it into the malevolent sensation"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 214260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "of the touch of the flame?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "Well you probably imagine that the nervous system in the body"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 219260.0,
      "end_time": 221260.0,
      "text": "is hardwired like your house."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 223260.0,
      "text": "In your house, wires run in the wall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 223260.0,
      "end_time": 226260.0,
      "text": "from the light switch to a junction box in the ceiling"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 226260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "and from the junction box to the light bulb."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "And when you turn the switch on, the light goes on."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 231260.0,
      "end_time": 234260.0,
      "text": "And when you turn the switch off, the light goes off."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 234260.0,
      "end_time": 238260.0,
      "text": "So people imagine the nervous system is just like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 238260.0,
      "end_time": 240260.0,
      "text": "If you hit your thumb with a hammer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 240260.0,
      "end_time": 243260.0,
      "text": "these wires in your arm -- that, of course, we call nerves --"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 243260.0,
      "end_time": 246260.0,
      "text": "transmit the information into the junction box in the spinal cord"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 246260.0,
      "end_time": 248260.0,
      "text": "where new wires, new nerves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 248260.0,
      "end_time": 250260.0,
      "text": "take the information up to the brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 250260.0,
      "end_time": 254260.0,
      "text": "where you become consciously aware that your thumb is now hurt."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 254260.0,
      "end_time": 256260.0,
      "text": "But the situation, of course, in the human body"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 256260.0,
      "end_time": 259260.0,
      "text": "is far more complicated than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 259260.0,
      "end_time": 261260.0,
      "text": "Instead of it being the case"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 261260.0,
      "end_time": 263260.0,
      "text": "that that junction box in the spinal cord"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 263260.0,
      "end_time": 266260.0,
      "text": "is just simple where one nerve connects with the next nerve"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 266260.0,
      "end_time": 268260.0,
      "text": "by releasing these little brown packets"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 268260.0,
      "end_time": 271260.0,
      "text": "of chemical information called neurotransmitters"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 271260.0,
      "end_time": 274260.0,
      "text": "in a linear one-on-one fashion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 274260.0,
      "end_time": 276260.0,
      "text": "in fact, what happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 276260.0,
      "end_time": 278260.0,
      "text": "is the neurotransmitters spill out in three dimensions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 278260.0,
      "end_time": 281260.0,
      "text": "laterally, vertically, up and down in the spinal cord --"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 281260.0,
      "end_time": 283260.0,
      "text": "and they start interacting"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 286260.0,
      "text": "with other adjacent cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 286260.0,
      "end_time": 288260.0,
      "text": "These cells, called glial cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 288260.0,
      "end_time": 290260.0,
      "text": "were once thought to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 290260.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "unimportant structural elements of the spinal cord"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 294260.0,
      "text": "that did nothing more than hold all the important things together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 294260.0,
      "end_time": 296260.0,
      "text": "like the nerves."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 296260.0,
      "end_time": 298260.0,
      "text": "But it turns out"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 298260.0,
      "end_time": 300260.0,
      "text": "the glial cells have a vital role"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 300260.0,
      "end_time": 302260.0,
      "text": "in the modulation, amplification"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 302260.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "and, in the case of pain, the distortion"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 308260.0,
      "text": "of sensory experiences."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 308260.0,
      "end_time": 310260.0,
      "text": "These glial cells become activated."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 310260.0,
      "end_time": 312260.0,
      "text": "Their DNA starts to synthesize new proteins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 312260.0,
      "end_time": 314260.0,
      "text": "which spill out"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 314260.0,
      "end_time": 316260.0,
      "text": "and interact with adjacent nerves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 316260.0,
      "end_time": 319260.0,
      "text": "and they start releasing their neurotransmitters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 319260.0,
      "end_time": 321260.0,
      "text": "and those neurotransmitters spill out"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 321260.0,
      "end_time": 324260.0,
      "text": "and activate adjacent glial cells, and so on and so forth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 324260.0,
      "end_time": 326260.0,
      "text": "until what we have"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 326260.0,
      "end_time": 328260.0,
      "text": "is a positive feedback loop."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 328260.0,
      "end_time": 330260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s almost as if somebody came into your home"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 330260.0,
      "end_time": 332260.0,
      "text": "and rewired your walls"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 332260.0,
      "end_time": 334260.0,
      "text": "so that the next time you turned on the light switch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 334260.0,
      "end_time": 336260.0,
      "text": "the toilet flushed three doors down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 336260.0,
      "end_time": 338260.0,
      "text": "or your dishwasher went on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 338260.0,
      "end_time": 340260.0,
      "text": "or your computer monitor turned off."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 340260.0,
      "end_time": 342260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s crazy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 342260.0,
      "end_time": 344260.0,
      "text": "but that&#39;s, in fact, what happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 344260.0,
      "end_time": 346260.0,
      "text": "with chronic pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 346260.0,
      "end_time": 349260.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s why pain becomes its own disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 349260.0,
      "end_time": 351260.0,
      "text": "The nervous system has plasticity."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 351260.0,
      "end_time": 353260.0,
      "text": "It changes, and it morphs"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 353260.0,
      "end_time": 355260.0,
      "text": "in response to stimuli."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 355260.0,
      "end_time": 357260.0,
      "text": "Well, what do we do about that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 357260.0,
      "end_time": 360260.0,
      "text": "What can we do in a case like Chandler&#39;s?"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 360260.0,
      "end_time": 362260.0,
      "text": "We treat these patients in a rather crude fashion"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 362260.0,
      "end_time": 364260.0,
      "text": "at this point in time."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 364260.0,
      "end_time": 367260.0,
      "text": "We treat them with symptom-modifying drugs --"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 367260.0,
      "end_time": 369260.0,
      "text": "painkillers --"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 369260.0,
      "end_time": 371260.0,
      "text": "which are, frankly, not very effective"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 371260.0,
      "end_time": 373260.0,
      "text": "for this kind of pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 373260.0,
      "end_time": 375260.0,
      "text": "We take nerves that are noisy and active"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 375260.0,
      "end_time": 377260.0,
      "text": "that should be quiet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 377260.0,
      "end_time": 379260.0,
      "text": "and we put them to sleep with local anesthetics."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 379260.0,
      "end_time": 382260.0,
      "text": "And most importantly, what we do"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 382260.0,
      "end_time": 386260.0,
      "text": "is we use a rigorous, and often uncomfortable, process"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 386260.0,
      "end_time": 389260.0,
      "text": "of physical therapy and occupational therapy"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 389260.0,
      "end_time": 392260.0,
      "text": "to retrain the nerves in the nervous system"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 392260.0,
      "end_time": 395260.0,
      "text": "to respond normally"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 395260.0,
      "end_time": 398260.0,
      "text": "to the activities and sensory experiences"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 398260.0,
      "end_time": 400260.0,
      "text": "that are part of everyday life."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 400260.0,
      "end_time": 402260.0,
      "text": "And we support all of that"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 402260.0,
      "end_time": 405260.0,
      "text": "with an intensive psychotherapy program"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 405260.0,
      "end_time": 408260.0,
      "text": "to address the despondency, despair and depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 408260.0,
      "end_time": 410260.0,
      "text": "that always accompanies"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 410260.0,
      "end_time": 412260.0,
      "text": "severe, chronic pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 412260.0,
      "end_time": 414260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s successful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 414260.0,
      "end_time": 416260.0,
      "text": "as you can see from this video of Chandler,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 416260.0,
      "end_time": 418260.0,
      "text": "who, two months after we first met her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 418260.0,
      "end_time": 420260.0,
      "text": "is now doings a back flip."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 420260.0,
      "end_time": 422260.0,
      "text": "And I had lunch with her yesterday"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 422260.0,
      "end_time": 425260.0,
      "text": "because she&#39;s a college student studying dance at Long Beach here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 425260.0,
      "end_time": 427260.0,
      "text": "and she&#39;s doing absolutely fantastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 427260.0,
      "end_time": 431260.0,
      "text": "But the future is actually even brighter."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 431260.0,
      "end_time": 434260.0,
      "text": "The future holds the promise"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 434260.0,
      "end_time": 436260.0,
      "text": "that new drugs will be developed"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 436260.0,
      "end_time": 439260.0,
      "text": "that are not symptom-modifying drugs"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 439260.0,
      "end_time": 441260.0,
      "text": "that simply mask the problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 441260.0,
      "end_time": 443260.0,
      "text": "as we have now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 443260.0,
      "end_time": 446260.0,
      "text": "but that will be disease-modifying drugs"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 446260.0,
      "end_time": 448260.0,
      "text": "that will actually go right to the root of the problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 448260.0,
      "end_time": 450260.0,
      "text": "and attack those glial cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 450260.0,
      "end_time": 452260.0,
      "text": "or those pernicious proteins"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 452260.0,
      "end_time": 455260.0,
      "text": "that the glial cells elaborate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 455260.0,
      "end_time": 458260.0,
      "text": "that spill over and cause this central nervous system wind-up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 458260.0,
      "end_time": 460260.0,
      "text": "or plasticity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 460260.0,
      "end_time": 462260.0,
      "text": "that so is capable"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 462260.0,
      "end_time": 464260.0,
      "text": "of distorting and amplifying"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 464260.0,
      "end_time": 466260.0,
      "text": "the sensory experience that we call pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 466260.0,
      "end_time": 468260.0,
      "text": "So I have hope"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 468260.0,
      "end_time": 470260.0,
      "text": "that in the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 470260.0,
      "end_time": 473260.0,
      "text": "the prophetic words of George Carlin will be realized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 473260.0,
      "end_time": 475260.0,
      "text": "who said, \"My philosophy:"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 475260.0,
      "end_time": 478260.0,
      "text": "No pain, no pain.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 479260.0,
      "end_time": 481260.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 481260.0,
      "end_time": 487260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}